{"tid":506631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蘋民爆料】屯門公屋叫價800萬 市民:「為之震驚」","createTime":"2017-12-22T11:36:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T01:53:40.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"9f8f7d48bfcfb415071da9cb751617e0de90f562","tid":506631,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171222/large/1513937352_8a56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171222%2Flarge%2F1513937352_8a56.jpg&h=0ad980d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即時財經  2017-12-22 17:20:53 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建生邨於1989年落成，由四幢公屋組成。房委會資料顯示，截至今年9月，建生邨租住認可人口為1,200人。<br />\n本報接獲《蘋果日報》讀者爆料，指「屯門公屋叫價驚見800萬」。有讀者本周發現祥益地產網站，屯門公屋建生邨有業主嘗試以自由市場叫價高達800萬元放盤，形容為之震驚，所以資助房屋已不再是窮人恩物，可見現在香港的樓市狀態是極為扭曲，以及其瘋狂程度已達到無人可控制之境地。<br />\n<br />\n本報進一步跟進，祥益地產網站的而且確出現建生邨叫價800萬元的癲價放盤，單位實用面積544方呎，呎價高達14,706元，媲美市區部份藍籌屋苑。如荔枝角美孚新邨，中原數據顯示其現時平均呎價12,366元。<br />\n<br />\n祥益地產黃慶德表示，該屯門叫價800萬元公屋，為建生邨泰生樓高層8室，本月初才放盤，業主同時正辦理居二市場出售證，綠表亦天價放盤，開價400萬元，較市價約300萬元貴逾三成。代理則解釋該單位於自由市場竟敢開價800萬元，據知是建生邨補價地價折扣較高。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，這間屯門800萬公屋，業主1998年向房屋署僅以16.24萬元買入單位自住，若以是次綠表叫價計算，較其買入價加價近24倍。<br />\n<br />\n目前全港最貴公屋是大圍顯徑邨，一個實用面積490方呎於今年11月以530萬元易手。<br />\n<br />\n代理表示，現時建生邨同面積連地價放盤不足5個，入場費大約480萬元。<br />\n<br />\n樓市瘋狂，各區均出現公屋天價放盤。盛產公屋王的鑽石山鳳德邨，驚見叫價近600萬元的綠表放盤。富誠地產林凱薇表示，鳳德邨雪鳳樓高層3室，實用面積598方呎，居二市場叫價599萬元，呎價10,017元，樓價及呎價均挑戰全港最貴未補價公屋。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果財經，關心你飯碗<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyatm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyatm&d=u0kssre03PlL57ZHWxc29C7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=55f95a68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyatm</a>"},{"pid":"810fe876dfdee3e3c8037ea78895e9585f023c42","tid":506631,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:39:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171222/57614614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171222%2F57614614&d=u0kssre03PlL57ZHWxc29C7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=206b03e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171222%2F57614614&h=874989cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171222/57614614</a>"},{"pid":"8f5f5a73e278646155d70da6efcc43052343650b","tid":506631,"uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:39:34.000Z","msg":"有瓏門唔住買殘舊公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"405f785f78efe5c66cc7e07b4fc20dca081d0d71","tid":506631,"uid":75072,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:39:53.000Z","msg":"傻閪先買"},{"pid":"48b9d3650df4b24625859522c31af80720ee0c87","tid":506631,"uid":71864,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:41:30.000Z","msg":"有人買先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a775d992cf558e42a00992ce1954f0dc6640e13a","tid":506631,"uid":106340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:42:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd6e2e82f94df227105c3e4545127b1b953baf33","tid":506631,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:42:21.000Z","msg":"呢幾日唱到好行既天生樓五百幾呎又係八球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8551f8d13a34ceedeaaccd6b7e77e2d556534f","tid":506631,"uid":20898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:43:47.000Z","msg":"洗黑錢？"},{"pid":"05a17ce268767a6e755b21b85a6f39ee8b56098c","tid":506631,"uid":42188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:43:50.000Z","msg":"做新聞啫<br />\n唔出多d呢d新聞<br />\nd灓單位私樓邊有人買"},{"pid":"9f4d75881cc5c73ec135302cb6ea